{
  "code": 200,
  "status": "OK",
  "data": {
    "number": 51,
    "name": "سُورَةُ الذَّارِيَاتِ",
    "englishName": "Adh-Dhaariyat",
    "englishNameTranslation": "The Winnowing Winds",
    "revelationType": "Meccan",
    "numberOfAyahs": 60,
    "ayahs": [
      {
        "number": 4676,
        "text": "By the swift scatterers",
        "numberInSurah": 1,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4677,
        "text": "and the burden-bearers",
        "numberInSurah": 2,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4678,
        "text": "and the smooth runners",
        "numberInSurah": 3,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4679,
        "text": "and the partitioners,",
        "numberInSurah": 4,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4680,
        "text": "surely that you are promised is true,",
        "numberInSurah": 5,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4681,
        "text": "and surely the Doom is about to fall!",
        "numberInSurah": 6,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 520,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4682,
        "text": "By heaven with all its tracks",
        "numberInSurah": 7,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4683,
        "text": "surely you speak at variance,",
        "numberInSurah": 8,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4684,
        "text": "and perverted therefrom are some.",
        "numberInSurah": 9,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4685,
        "text": "Perish the conjecturers",
        "numberInSurah": 10,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4686,
        "text": "who are dazed in perplexity",
        "numberInSurah": 11,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4687,
        "text": "asking, 'When shall be the Day of Doom?'",
        "numberInSurah": 12,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4688,
        "text": "Upon the day when they shall be tried at the Fire:",
        "numberInSurah": 13,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4689,
        "text": "'Taste your trial! This is that you were seeking to hasten.'",
        "numberInSurah": 14,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4690,
        "text": "Surely the godfearing shall be among gardens and fountains",
        "numberInSurah": 15,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4691,
        "text": "taking whatsoever their Lord has given them; they were good-doers before that.",
        "numberInSurah": 16,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4692,
        "text": "Little of the night would they slumber,",
        "numberInSurah": 17,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4693,
        "text": "and in the mornings they would ask for forgiveness;",
        "numberInSurah": 18,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4694,
        "text": "and the beggar and the outcast had a share in their wealth.",
        "numberInSurah": 19,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4695,
        "text": "In the earth are signs for those having sure faith;",
        "numberInSurah": 20,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4696,
        "text": "and in your selves; what, do you not see?",
        "numberInSurah": 21,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4697,
        "text": "And in heaven is your provision, and that you are promised.",
        "numberInSurah": 22,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4698,
        "text": "So by the Lord of heaven and earth, it is as surely true as that you have speech.",
        "numberInSurah": 23,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 455,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4699,
        "text": "Hast thou received the story of the honoured guests of Abraham?",
        "numberInSurah": 24,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4700,
        "text": "When they entered unto him, saying 'Peace!' he said 'Peace! You are a people unknown to me.'",
        "numberInSurah": 25,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4701,
        "text": "Then he turned to his household and brought a fattened calf,",
        "numberInSurah": 26,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4702,
        "text": "and he laid it before them saying, 'Will you not eat?'",
        "numberInSurah": 27,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4703,
        "text": "Then he conceived a fear of them. They said, 'Be not afraid!' And they gave him good tidings of a cunning boy.",
        "numberInSurah": 28,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4704,
        "text": "Then came forward his wife, clamouring, and she smote her face, and said, 'An old woman, barren!'",
        "numberInSurah": 29,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4705,
        "text": "They said, 'So says thy Lord; He is the All-wise, the All-knowing.'",
        "numberInSurah": 30,
        "juz": 26,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 521,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 208,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4706,
        "text": "Said he, 'And what is your business, envoys?'",
        "numberInSurah": 31,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4707,
        "text": "They said, 'We have been sent to a people of sinners,",
        "numberInSurah": 32,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4708,
        "text": "to loose upon them stones of clay",
        "numberInSurah": 33,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4709,
        "text": "marked with thy Lord for the prodigal.",
        "numberInSurah": 34,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4710,
        "text": "So We brought forth such believers as were in it,",
        "numberInSurah": 35,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4711,
        "text": "but We found not therein except one house of those that have surrendered themselves.",
        "numberInSurah": 36,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4712,
        "text": "And therein We left a sign to those who fear the painful chastisement.",
        "numberInSurah": 37,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4713,
        "text": "And also in Moses, when We sent him unto Pharaoh, with a clear authority,",
        "numberInSurah": 38,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4714,
        "text": "but he turned his back, with his court, saying, 'A sorcerer, or a man possessed!'",
        "numberInSurah": 39,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4715,
        "text": "So We seized him and his hosts, and We cast them into the sea, and he blameworthy.",
        "numberInSurah": 40,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4716,
        "text": "And also in Ad, when We loosed against them the withering wind",
        "numberInSurah": 41,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4717,
        "text": "that left nothing it came upon, but made it as stuff decayed.",
        "numberInSurah": 42,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4718,
        "text": "And also in Thamood, when it was said to them, 'Take your enjoyment for a while!'",
        "numberInSurah": 43,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4719,
        "text": "Then they turned in disdain from the commandment of their Lord, and the thunderbolt took them and they themselves beholding",
        "numberInSurah": 44,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4720,
        "text": "and they were not able to stand upright, and were not helped.",
        "numberInSurah": 45,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4721,
        "text": "And the people of Noah before; surely they were an ungodly people.",
        "numberInSurah": 46,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 456,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4722,
        "text": "And heaven -- We built it with might, and We extend it wide.",
        "numberInSurah": 47,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4723,
        "text": "And the earth -- We spread it forth; O excellent Smoothers!",
        "numberInSurah": 48,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4724,
        "text": "And of everything created We two kinds; haply you will remember.",
        "numberInSurah": 49,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4725,
        "text": "Therefore flee unto God! I am a clear warner from Him to you.",
        "numberInSurah": 50,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4726,
        "text": "And set not up with God another god; I am a clear warner from Him to you.",
        "numberInSurah": 51,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 522,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4727,
        "text": "Even so not a Messenger came to those before them but they said, 'A sorcerer, or a man possessed!'",
        "numberInSurah": 52,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4728,
        "text": "What, have they bequeathed it one to another? Nay, but they are an insolent people.",
        "numberInSurah": 53,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4729,
        "text": "So turn thou from them; thou wilt not be reproached.",
        "numberInSurah": 54,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4730,
        "text": "And remind; the Reminder profits the believers.",
        "numberInSurah": 55,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4731,
        "text": "I have not created jinn and mankind except to serve Me.",
        "numberInSurah": 56,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4732,
        "text": "I desire of them no provision, neither do I desire that they should feed Me.",
        "numberInSurah": 57,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4733,
        "text": "Surely God is the All-provider, the Possessor of Strength, the Ever-Sure.",
        "numberInSurah": 58,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4734,
        "text": "The evildoers shall have their portion, like the portion of their fellows; so let them not hasten Me!",
        "numberInSurah": 59,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      },
      {
        "number": 4735,
        "text": "So woe to the unbelievers, for that day of theirs that they are promised.",
        "numberInSurah": 60,
        "juz": 27,
        "manzil": 7,
        "page": 523,
        "ruku": 457,
        "hizbQuarter": 209,
        "sajda": false
      }
    ],
    "edition": {
      "identifier": "en.arberry",
      "language": "en",
      "name": "Arberry",
      "englishName": "A. J. Arberry",
      "format": "text",
      "type": "translation",
      "direction": "ltr"
    }
  }
}